{"type": "article", "id": 20397, "title": "这个木茶几，看起来像是一座快要倾覆的城市", "description": "设计师以《盗梦空间》为灵感。然而，这茶几看起来并不怎么“盗梦空间”啦。", "date": "2016-01-09T07:30:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1525, "name": "茶几"}, {"id": 11006, "name": "盗梦空间"}, {"id": 767, "name": "家具设计"}, {"id": 21750, "name": "塞浦路斯"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 14, "praise_count": 253, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702122303TcgNztYO1KivfWsH.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t塞浦路斯设计师 <a href=\"http://www.mousarris.com/\">Stelios Mousarris</a> 受到 2010 年大热的影片《盗梦空间》影响，设计了一款弯曲的茶几，<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2016/01/05/a-city-landscape-is-curved-within-this-coffee-table/\" target=\"_blank\">名叫 <span style=\"text-align:left;\"> Wave City </span></a>。把这茶几放在客厅里或许挺酷，但好难为它寻找相搭配的家具啊！\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122257Gu4lKt6voq1PaZC9.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"449\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.56125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span style=\"text-align:left;\">设计师将城市景象倾覆了过来</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021222583R7dJzpeqbSwD6Vf.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"449\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.56125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">总体来看，茶几就是长这样了\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122258V4gKkMWOclpPrE9z.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"449\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.56125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">精细的细节\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122259n16ZcXSM2vbtNjph.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"449\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.56125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t按照设计师的说法，这茶几采用了复合板材，在制作的过程中，还借用了 3D 打印技术。设计师 Stelios Mousarris 曾在 Fosters and Partners 担任制模师，还在设 Duffylondon 工作过，2014 年他自立门户，创建了 Mousarris ，主要从事家具设计，以下是他完成的家具作品，非常讲究造型和弧度：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122259elpzJ6KgmyabsX7I.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"547\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.56979167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122300iRru0Ux2LNwOhEfj.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"541\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.56354167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t他偶尔还会设计一些餐厅及议事空间：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021223006vlqG1VHoOxsc0zD.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"350\" title=\"Duffy London\" alt=\"Duffy London\" data-ratio=\"0.36458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Duffy London</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122301OjPIs0VxMiKeGzXp.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" title=\"伯明翰餐厅 Pirifino\" alt=\"伯明翰餐厅 Pirifino\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>伯明翰餐厅 Pirifino</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021223016AEZbN8workyChHR.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"891\" title=\" Pirifino\" alt=\" Pirifino\" data-ratio=\"0.928125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> Pirifino</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122302I8deHSiNqWjC9uAh.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"607\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021223021sPOmXSVEC5gizoI.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"607\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2016/01/05/a-city-landscape-is-curved-within-this-coffee-table/\" target=\"_blank\">contemporist</a> \r\n</p>\n\n"}